	<div class="header"><h1>CDX</h1></div><div class="content">
	<div class="image"><img alt="" height="239" src="/history/ancient/romans/images/launch_cdx.jpg" width="304"/>
	</div><p>A sacrificial blade forged at the birth of the Roman empire holds the key to an ancient and bloody conspiracy that threatens to erupt into the present day. </p><p>Stranded in 21st century Tunis, Adam Foster is plunged into a world of greed, betrayal and murder. But who has the blade, and can the killers be stopped?</p><div class="launch_button_large"><div class="end"> </div><a href="/history/interactive/games/cdx/index_embed.shtml" title="Launch the application">Launch the game</a></div>
	
